@page
@using FeatureRequest.FeatureRequests
@using FeatureRequest.Localization
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Localization
@inject IHtmlLocalizer<FeatureRequestResource> L
@model FeatureRequest.Web.Pages.FeatureRequests.EditModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = L["EditPage:Title"];
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card shadow">
                <div class="card-header bg-warning text-dark">
                    <h3><i class="fa fa-edit"></i> @L["EditPage:Header"]</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">

                    <form method="post">

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="Request.Title" class="form-label">@L["EditPage:TitleLabel"]</label>
                            <input asp-for="Request.Title" class="form-control" />
                            <span asp-validation-for="Request.Title" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="Request.CategoryId" class="form-label">@L["EditPage:CategoryLabel"]</label>
                            <select asp-for="Request.CategoryId" asp-items="Html.GetEnumSelectList<FeatureRequestCategory>()" class="form-select"></select>
                            <span asp-validation-for="Request.CategoryId" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="Request.Status" class="form-label">@L["EditPage:StatusLabel"]</label>
                            <select asp-for="Request.Status" asp-items="Html.GetEnumSelectList<FeatureRequestStatus>()" class="form-select"></select>
                            <span asp-validation-for="Request.Status" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label asp-for="Request.Description" class="form-label">@L["EditPage:DescriptionLabel"]</label>
                            <textarea asp-for="Request.Description" class="form-control" rows="5"></textarea>
                            <span asp-validation-for="Request.Description" class="text-danger"></span>
                        </div>

                        <hr />

                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                            <a href="/FeatureRequests/Detail?id=@Model.Id" class="btn btn-secondary">@L["EditPage:Cancel"]</a>

                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning px-4">
                                <i class="fa fa-save"></i> @L["EditPage:SaveChanges"]
                            </button>
                        </div>

                    </form>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>